Privacy Policy

At Gen AI Editor, we value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle your data.

1. What We Collect

  • Email (for feedback or contact forms)
  • Uploaded files (for editing only)
  • Browser info (to improve experience)

2. How We Use It

We use your data only to provide editing features. No selling or sharing with others.

3. File Handling

All uploaded content is auto-deleted after editing. We do not save anything.

4. Third-party Services

We may use cloud services for speed. These follow safe privacy rules (like GDPR).

5. Your Rights

You can ask us to delete any personal data by visiting the Contact page.

6. Updates

We might update this policy if features change. Last updated: June 30, 2025

); }
